    "They used the OpenAI Gym task ecosystem (Brockman et al. 2016).",
    "Neves et al. (2022) proposed a method named COMPact Experience Replay (COMPER) to improve the model of experience memory and make ER feasible (and more efficient) using smaller amounts of data."
